::Hot Rod::

He drops to his back and manages to catch the missile between his hands.
"Sweet..."
The optic blast hits the missile and it blows. Hot Rod is shot several
feet away, but still in one piece. He gets up, and shoots two missiles
back at Unicron. He runs back up and starts shooting laser blasts.
